---

### Phase 1 — Foundation & Auth

#### [NEW] `prisma/schema.prisma`
- Full database schema as shown in the ER diagram above
- All models, enums, and relations

#### [NEW] `prisma/seed.ts`
- Seeds the database with: rooms, an initial admin account, sample data for testing

#### [NEW] `src/lib/prisma.ts`
- Prisma client singleton (prevents connection exhaustion in dev)

#### [NEW] `src/lib/auth.ts`
- NextAuth.js configuration with credentials provider
- Session includes user role for RBAC
- Password hashing with bcrypt

#### [NEW] `src/lib/permissions.ts`
- Helper functions: `canReviewProjects(role)`, `canManageUsers(role)`, `canSubmitProjects(role)`
- Middleware-style route protection

#### [NEW] `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx`
- Clean login page with ASC logo
- Email + password form
- Redirects to dashboard on success

#### [NEW] `src/app/globals.css`
- CSS custom properties (design tokens): colors, spacing, typography, shadows
- Base reset and typography (using Inter from Google Fonts)
- French-language-friendly typography settings
- Print stylesheet (`@media print`) that hides sidebar, navigation, and non-essential UI

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx`
- Authenticated layout wrapper
- Sidebar navigation (French labels): Tableau de bord, Projets, Étudiants, Personnel, Calendrier, Discussions, Revue, Paramètres
- Top header with user info, notifications bell, logout
- Mobile-responsive: sidebar collapses to hamburger menu

---

### Phase 2 — Project Management (Core Module)

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/page.tsx` — Dashboard Home
- Role-aware dashboard:
  - **Admin/Committee**: Review queue summary, upcoming sessions, recent discussions
  - **Instructor**: My projects, my upcoming sessions, notifications
- Quick stats cards: active projects, enrolled students, pending reviews

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/projets/page.tsx` — Project List
- Filterable/searchable table of all projects
- Status filter (Draft, Active, Under Review, etc.)
- Type filter (Workshop, Course, Activity)
- Each row shows: title, type, status badge, lead instructor, dates, enrollment count

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/projets/nouveau/page.tsx` — New Project Form
- **Multi-step form** (not one massive page):
  1. **Informations de base**: Title, description, type, age group, language
  2. **Horaire**: Start/end dates, recurring sessions, room assignment (with conflict check)
  3. **Équipe**: Assign lead, co-instructors, helpers (from staff list, with conflict detection)
  4. **Budget**: Registration fee, projected costs, revenue estimate
  5. **Marketing**: Public description, promo notes, enrollment dates, capacity
  6. **Révision**: Summary of all fields before submission
- Save as Draft at any step, or Submit for Review at the end

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/projets/[id]/page.tsx` — Project Detail
- Full project view with all info organized in tabs or sections
- Status timeline showing lifecycle progression
- Budget tracker: projected vs. actual (bar chart, simple CSS — no chart library)
- Enrolled students list with enrollment status
- Assigned staff list
- Session schedule
- Discussion thread (project-specific)
- Action buttons based on role and status:
  - Instructor: Edit (if Draft), Submit for Review
  - Committee: Approve / Reject / Request Revision
  - Admin: All of the above + Archive / Delete

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/projets/route.ts` + `[id]/route.ts`
- CRUD endpoints for projects
- Status transition validation (e.g., can't go from Draft → Active without approval)
- Conflict detection on session/room assignment

---

