- Conflict detection endpoint for staff scheduling

---

### Phase 4 — Calendar System

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/calendrier/page.tsx`
- **Three views**: Day, Week, Month (toggle buttons)
- **Filters**: Room, instructor, project, date range
- **Room view**: Columns = rooms, rows = time slots (like Google Calendar's "resource" view)
- Color-coded by project (each project gets a consistent color)
- Click a session → modal with details + link to project
- Conflict detection: visual warning if two sessions overlap in the same room

#### [NEW] `src/components/calendar/` — Calendar Components
- `CalendarGrid.tsx`: Base grid layout using CSS Grid
- `DayView.tsx`: Single day, all rooms as columns
- `WeekView.tsx`: 7-day view, filterable
- `MonthView.tsx`: Traditional month grid with session dots
- `PrintableCalendar.tsx`: Clean, minimal layout optimized for `@media print`

#### Print Layouts
- **Weekly schedule**: Clean grid, black-and-white friendly, room labels
- **Room-by-room daily**: One page per room showing the day's schedule
- **Instructor schedule**: One page per instructor showing their day
- All triggered via a "Imprimer" (Print) button that applies print CSS and calls `window.print()`

---

### Phase 5 — Discussions & Notifications

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/discussions/page.tsx` — Discussion List
- General (non-project) discussions
- Project-specific discussions linked from each project page
- Each thread shows: title, last message preview, unread count, tags used

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/discussions/[id]/page.tsx` — Discussion Thread
- Chronological message list
- Each message shows: author, timestamp, content, tag badge (Question / Feedback / Decision / Action Item)
- Compose box at the bottom with tag selector

#### [NEW] Notification System
- `src/app/api/notifications/route.ts` — Fetch/mark-read endpoints
- Bell icon in header with unread count badge
- Notification dropdown: list of recent notifications with links
- Triggered by: new discussion message in your threads, project status change, new project submitted for review

---

### Phase 6 — Governance & Approvals

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/revue/page.tsx` — Review Queue
- Committee-only view (redirects instructors away)
- Table of all projects with status `SUBMITTED` or `UNDER_REVIEW`
- Each row: project title, submitted by, submitted date, type, action buttons
- Click → goes to project detail page with review form

#### Review Form (within Project Detail page)
- Structured form: Approve / Reject / Request Revision (radio)
- Mandatory text field for notes/reasoning
- Submit creates a `ReviewAction` record with timestamp and reviewer name
- Updates project status accordingly
- Notifies the project creator

#### Audit Log
- Visible on each project detail page under a "Historique" tab
- Chronological list of all `ReviewAction` entries
- Shows: action, reviewer name, notes, timestamp

---

### Phase 7 — Settings & Admin

#### [NEW] `src/app/(dashboard)/parametres/page.tsx`
- **Admin only**
- User management: create/edit/deactivate user accounts, assign roles
- Room management: add/edit/remove rooms
- System settings: centre name, default language, etc.

